Class Summary
Class Description
AboutFrame
AboutFrame is an enhanced version of JFrame , which displays information about the program.
AppStart
AppStart is a class , which launches the application.
AuthorFrame
AuthorFrame is an enhanced version of JFrame , which displays information about the author.
Controller
Controller is a class , which contains a method to convert one length unit to another.
Converter
Converter is a class , which contains the fields intended for converting values and methods for their access.
MainFrame
MainFrame is an enhanced version of JFrame , which allows you to convert units of lengths (millimeters, centimeters, meters, kilometers, feet, miles).
StartFrame
A StartFrame is an extended version of JFrame that shown while the MainFrame is creating.
